[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0452","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0267","title":"NCSA HTTPd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.3 版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，进而实现远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0267"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.227","remediation":"NCSA HTTPd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。迁移后需重新配置虚拟主机、访问控制和 SSL 证书，并关闭旧服务器上的 80/443 端口。如无法立即迁移，可在防火墙层面限制对 80 端口的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0267","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21050","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0267","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-1999-0267.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0470","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0282","title":"（已废弃）CVE-1999-0282 错误合并 SunOS loadmodule 两个独立漏洞的无效编号","description":"CVE-1999-0282 是一个已被官方驳回（REJECTED）的 CVE 编号，原因是它错误地将 CVE-1999-1584 和 CVE-1999-1586 两个不同漏洞的参考信息和描述合并为一条记录。NVD 已移除该编号下所有描述与引用，禁止继续使用。该编号不指向任何真实存在的漏洞，不存在可利用的攻击面或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0282"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:56.640","remediation":"CVE-1999-0282 已被撤销，请勿使用此编号。实际漏洞分别对应 CVE-1999-1584（SunOS 4.1.1–4.1.3c 及 Open Windows 3.0 中 loadmodule/modload 的本地权限提升）和 CVE-1999-1586（SunOS 4.1.x 中 xnews 调用的 loadmodule 未正确清理环境变量导致本地提权）。Sun 当时发布了补丁（如 Sun patch 100124-01），CERT 也发布了公告 CA-1993-18，但这些补丁现已无法获取。由于 SunOS 4.x 早已停止支持，建议将仍在运行的 SunOS 4.1.x 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Solaris 11、Linux 或 \\*BSD），同时严格控制 setuid/setgid 二进制文件的权限以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0993","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0667","title":"TCP/IP ARP协议缓存投毒欺骗漏洞","description":"ARP（地址解析协议）协议设计上缺乏身份验证机制，在同一广播域内的任何攻击者均可向目标主机发送伪造的 ARP 应答报文，毒化其 ARP 缓存表，将目标 IP 地址与攻击者 MAC 地址关联。该漏洞影响所有使用 ARP 协议的网络设备，攻击者无需认证即可实施中间人攻击、IP 地址欺骗或拒绝服务攻击，是局域网中最基础且广泛存在的协议层安全问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0667"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.363","remediation":"在关键网段交换机启用动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 和 DHCP Snooping，阻止伪造 ARP 报文；对核心资产配置静态 ARP 条目；部署 ARP 防火墙或 arpwatch 等监控工具检测异常 ARP 变化；使用 IPsec/MACsec 加密通信链路，降低中间人攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602880019797&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0192","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0079","title":"Sun Solaris 7/8 FTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7 和 Solaris 8 系统的 FTP 服务器存在资源耗尽漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送大量 PASV 命令，导致服务器可用端口被迅速耗尽，从而使合法用户无法建立新的数据连接，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用门槛低，仅需网络可达即可触发，影响运行上述 Solaris 版本的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0079"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.890","remediation":"建议安装 Sun 官方补丁 ID 106222-02 (Solaris 7) 或 106223-02 (Solaris 8)，限制单连接内 PASV 命令的并发端口数。也可在 in.ftpd 配置中降低 PASV 最小端口范围或缩短空闲端口超时。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 控制连接速率作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0079"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0258","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0115","title":"IBM AIX bugfiler 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x 操作系统中的 bugfiler 程序存在任意文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可创建或覆盖系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 3.x 版本，攻击者仅需本地账户即可利用，无需用户交互，危害较高，CVSS 评分 7.2。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0115"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.230","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.1.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续发行版中修复。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/bugfiler` 移除 setuid 特权位，防止本地用户通过 bugfiler 获取 root Shell；若无需使用 bugfiler 工具，可直接 `chmod 700 /usr/bin/bugfiler` 限制仅 root 可执行。请评估是否需同时更新 `bos.rte.security` 文件集的相关安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1800","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0115","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0115.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0353","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0177","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 服务器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WebSite Web 服务器中的 uploader 程序存在任意文件上传漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的上传请求，将恶意可执行文件上传至服务器任意目录并远程执行，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响早期版本的 WebSite 服务器软件，攻击者只需能够网络访问目标服务器即可发起攻击，利用方式简单、危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0177"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.913","remediation":"建议立即升级至 O'Reilly WebSite Professional 2.x（该版本已修复 uploader 漏洞）；如无法升级，可直接删除或禁用 webroot 下的 uploader.exe/cgi 程序，并在 Web 服务器或防火墙层面限制对 uploader 相关路径的访问。由于该产品已终止技术支持（EOL），长期解决方案是迁移至仍在安全维护期的 Web 服务器（如 Apache、Nginx 或 IIS）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0177"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0374","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0191","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 newdsn.exe 文件创建漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 的 newdsn.exe CGI 脚本存在文件创建/覆盖漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求利用此脚本，在服务器上任意创建或覆盖文件，可能导致系统配置被篡改或敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击复杂度较低，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0191"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.367","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 3.0 服务器上的 newdsn.exe 文件或将其所在 cgi-bin 目录权限设置为禁止匿名访问；同时升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本以彻底消除该 CGI 脚本，或迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并启用最新安全配置。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 过滤规则拦截对 newdsn.exe 的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/275","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20309","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0191","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0191.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p6cp-hx87-7342/GHSA-p6cp-hx87-7342.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0191.yaml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/newdsn.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0374.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0374.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0179","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0179.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0071","title":"Apache HTTP Server Cookie 处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.1.1 及更早版本的 cookie 处理函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未对输入长度进行充分校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 Cookie 数据触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致 httpd 进程崩溃或潜在远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有运行受影响 Apache httpd 版本的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0071"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 cookie 处理函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。由于 1.2.0 版本也已停止维护，建议迁移至当前受支持的 Apache HTTP Server 版本（如 2.4.x），以确保获得持续的安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0071","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0179.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0302","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0302.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0148","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 CGI 处理程序远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统自带的 cgi-bin 处理器程序 handler 存在命令注入漏洞。该 CGI 程序未能正确过滤用户提供的 URL 参数，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，在受影响服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意系统命令。攻击复杂度低且无需身份验证，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0148"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5 或更高版本以修复 cgi-bin handler 的命令注入漏洞。如无法升级，在 /etc/cgi-bin/handler 配置中移除不必要的 CGI 映射，并在网络层面限制对 CGI 端口的访问。若环境允许，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/380","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19303"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19303"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0302.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0302.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0366","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0366.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0183","title":"Linux TFTP 实现目录遍历漏洞","description":"Linux系统的TFTP（Trivial File Transfer Protocol）实现中存在目录遍历漏洞，未限制文件访问路径。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过路径穿越技术访问TFTP根目录之外的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露，如密码文件等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0183"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复此漏洞的TFTP服务器版本（如tftp-hpa），或配置chroot环境将TFTP服务限制在指定目录内，并禁用符号链接跟随以防止目录遍历攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T21:58:50.651362824+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0366.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0422","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0422.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0237","title":"Guestbook CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Guestbook CGI 程序（Matt Wright 编写的 Perl 脚本）未对用户输入进行充分过滤和转义，远程攻击者可通过向表单字段提交特制的 shell 元字符实现命令注入，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务进程权限执行任意命令。此漏洞无需身份认证，利用门槛低，攻击者仅需构造恶意 HTTP 请求即可入侵服务器。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响大量使用该 CGI 程序的老旧 Web 服务器。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0237"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即删除或更换服务器上的 guestbook.cgi 脚本，该 CGI 程序已停止维护且无官方补丁。对用户输入进行严格过滤，移除 shell 元字符（|;`$等）。建议使用现代留言板系统替代，或通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 ScriptAlias 或 Nginx 禁止 CGI 执行）彻底禁用此脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0237","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0237","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0237.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p9x6-hv6c-rpfx/GHSA-p9x6-hv6c-rpfx.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/guestbook.nasl","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80893/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0422.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0081","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0024","title":"ISC BIND DNS 查询标识符可预测导致缓存投毒漏洞","description":"BIND DNS 服务器存在 DNS 缓存投毒漏洞，由于使用可预测的查询 ID 作为事务标识符，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送伪造的 DNS 响应报文，在无需认证的情况下实施缓存投毒攻击，将合法域名解析指向恶意 IP 地址，导致用户被重定向至恶意网站或遭受中间人攻击。该漏洞影响早期 BIND 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0024"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.577","remediation":"升级 BIND 至 4.9.7 或 8.2 及以上版本，该版本引入了随机化 DNS 查询 ID 机制，防止攻击者预测 ID 实施缓存投毒。若无法升级，可在 named.conf 中限制递归查询仅对受信任内部网段开放（allow-recursion），并在边界防火墙上阻断 UDP 53 端口的非授权外部访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0024"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0152","title":"Data General DG/UX finger 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"DG/UX 系统的 finger 服务程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 finger 服务发送包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制请求，利用服务程序对用户输入过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 finger 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 DG/UX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低，利用方式简单，影响较为广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0152"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.707","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（/etc/inetd.conf 中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd），或在防火墙层面阻止外部对 finger 端口（79/tcp）的访问。由于 DG/UX 已停止技术支持且无官方补丁，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0152"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0423","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0238","title":"PHP PHP/fi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 2.0 的 php.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用路径遍历技术读取服务器上的任意文件，包括敏感配置文件、密码文件等。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 2.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，危害较大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0238"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.650","remediation":"立即移除或禁用 PHP/fi 2.0 中的 php.cgi 脚本，升级至 PHP 3.0 或更高版本（PHP 3.0 起已重写架构并修复此目录遍历问题）。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中限制 php.cgi 仅访问指定目录，或通过 .htaccess / httpd.conf 禁止直接访问该脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0238","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0238","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0238.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0238.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2250/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0498","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0301","title":"Sun Solaris ps 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 以及 SGI IRIX 6.5.4 系统的 ps(1) 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 ps 命令传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的数据，实现权限提升。成功利用该漏洞可导致攻击者获取 root 权限，完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0301"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.370","remediation":"安装 Sun 补丁 105400-01（x86）或 105395-01（SPARC）修复 Solaris 2.5.1 的 ps 缓冲区溢出漏洞；SGI IRIX 6.5.4 应升级至 6.5.5 或更高版本。两款系统均已停止支持，建议迁移至现代操作系统。临时缓解措施可移除 ps 的 setuid 位：`chmod -s /usr/bin/ps`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/149","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19168"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml"}]